[30;1m111 | [0m[35m    # At most 2 iterations ought to be enough to converge. Before the loop, we[0m
[30;1m112 | [0m[35m    # know the start circle didn't keep containment after normal rounding; thus[0m
[30;1m113 | [0m[35m    # we continue adjusting by -/+ 1.0 until containment is restored.[0m
[30;1m114 | [0m[35m    # Normal rounding can at most move each coordinates -/+0.5; in the worst case[0m
[30;1m115 | [0m[35m    # both the start and end circle's centres and radii will be rounded in opposite[0m
[30;1m116 | [0m[35m    # directions, e.g. when they move along a 45 degree diagonal:[0m
[30;1m117 | [0m[35m    #   c0 = (1.5, 1.5) ===> (2.0, 2.0)[0m

[30;1m315 | [0m[35mHow to make a new release[0m
[30;1m316 | [0m[35m~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[0m
[30;1m317 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m318 | [0m[35m1) Update ``NEWS.rst`` with all the changes since the last release. Write a[0m
[30;1m319 | [0m[35m   changelog entry for each PR, with one or two short sentences summarizing it,[0m
[30;1m320 | [0m[35m   as well as links to the PR and relevant issues addressed by the PR. Do not[0m
[30;1m321 | [0m[35m   put a new title, the next command will do it for you.[0m

[30;1m315 | [0m[35mHow to make a new release[0m
[30;1m316 | [0m[35m~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[0m
[30;1m317 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m318 | [0m[35m1) Update ``NEWS.rst`` with all the changes since the last release. Write a[0m
[30;1m319 | [0m[35m   changelog entry for each PR, with one or two short sentences summarizing it,[0m
[30;1m320 | [0m[35m   as well as links to the PR and relevant issues addressed by the PR. Do not[0m
[30;1m321 | [0m[35m   put a new title, the next command will do it for you.[0m

[30;1m225 | [0m[35mHow to make a new release[0m
[30;1m226 | [0m[35m~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[0m
[30;1m227 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m228 | [0m[35m1) Update ``NEWS.rst`` with all the changes since the last release. Write a[0m
[30;1m229 | [0m[35m   changelog entry for each PR, with one or two short sentences summarizing it,[0m
[30;1m230 | [0m[35m   as well as links to the PR and relevant issues addressed by the PR. Do not[0m
[30;1m231 | [0m[35m   put a new title, the next command will do it for you.[0m
